[Off Topic] Yahoo changing Groups services?

Yahoo has a survey in which they propose reducing storage limits
for its groups, and charging for more storage and premium services.
I think it important that everyone who uses Yahoo Groups to have an
opportunity to be heard. Here's the link:

http://sweepstakes.yahoo.com/groupspremiumsurvey2
